程序包 cn.edu.gxust.jiweihuang.java.pointer.cminpack

类 JavaMinpack

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.edu.gxust.jiweihuang.java.pointer.cminpack.JavaMinpack
  • public class JavaMinpack
extends Object
    类JavaMinpackPointer采用Java语言和JavaPointer库 重新实现了cminpack库。

    cminpack包是一种C语言实现，源于Fortran编写的minpack库。

    从以下版本开始:
    20191102
    作者:
    JiweiHuang

      • doubleEpsilon

        public static double doubleEpsilon()
        The round-off unit is a number R which is used for representing the precision of the computer's arithmetic,that means:

        1 < 1 + R, but 1 = ( 1 + R / 2 ).

        返回:
        round-off unit of double
